Tusk Says Higher Pay for Polish Police ‘Absolutely Necessary’

-- B y   D a v i d   M c Q u a i d
-- 
2011-10-13T11:49:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/tusk-says-higher-pay-for-polish-police-absolutely-necessary-.html
Pay increases for Polish police are
“absolutely necessary,” Prime Minister Donald Tusk told
reporters today at a news conference in Warsaw. He didn’t
specify when or by how much police wages would be increased.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
